      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum mechanics assumptions (linear elastic titanium, nonlinear UHMWPE block) justified by literature and material coupon data.",
      "rationale": "Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) rod and screw modeled as linear elastic based on strain levels remaining below yield in the elastic regime of interest. UHMWPE vertebral body surrogate modeled with bilinear plasticity calibrated to coupon test data. Model form is consistent with prior published validation studies for F1717 constructs. Requirement level 3 is met."
