      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from traceable coupon tests or peer-reviewed literature with uncertainty quantification.",
      "rationale": "Elastic moduli and yield strengths for Ti-6Al-4V and UHMWPE sourced from traceable coupon test reports supplied by DePuy Synthes. Coefficient of friction for screw-rod interface set to 0.25 ± 0.05 based on published tribology literature. Sensitivity analysis confirmed QoI insensitivity to ±20% variation in friction coefficient. Requirement level 3 is met."
