      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "N≥10 experimental specimens from at least two independent lots; dimensional inspection confirms geometry within drawing tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (FDA CDRH and DePuy Synthes). Specimens drawn from two manufacturing lots. Dimensional inspection confirmed all screws within ±0.05 mm of nominal geometry. Requirement level 3 is met."
