      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric E/uval < 1.96 for all primary QoIs; percentage difference < 10%.",
      "rationale": "E/uval values of 1.31, 1.55, and 1.18 computed for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement respectively, all below the 1.96 threshold. Percentage differences of 4.2%, 7.8%, and 6.1% are within the 10% acceptance bound. Requirement level 3 is met."
